{"sn35.136:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 35.136 ","sn35.136:0.2":"14. Devadahavagga ","sn35.136:0.3":"Pathamaruparamasutta ","sn35.136:1.1":"“Ruparama, bhikkhave, devamanussa ruparata rupasammudita. ","sn35.136:1.2":"Rupaviparinamaviraganirodha dukkha, bhikkhave, devamanussa viharanti. ","sn35.136:1.3":"Saddarama, bhikkhave, devamanussa saddarata saddasammudita. ","sn35.136:1.4":"Saddaviparinamaviraganirodha dukkha, bhikkhave, devamanussa viharanti. ","sn35.136:1.5":"Gandharama … ","sn35.136:1.6":"rasarama … ","sn35.136:1.7":"photthabbarama … ","sn35.136:1.8":"dhammarama, bhikkhave, devamanussa dhammarata dhammasammudita. ","sn35.136:1.9":"Dhammaviparinamaviraganirodha dukkha, bhikkhave, devamanussa viharanti. ","sn35.136:1.10":"Tathagato ca kho, bhikkhave, araham sammasambuddho rupanam samudayanca atthangamanca assadanca adinavanca nissarananca yathabhutam viditva na ruparamo na ruparato na rupasammudito. ","sn35.136:1.11":"Rupaviparinamaviraganirodha sukho, bhikkhave, tathagato viharati. ","sn35.136:1.12":"Saddanam … ","sn35.136:1.13":"gandhanam … ","sn35.136:1.14":"rasanam … ","sn35.136:1.15":"photthabbanam … ","sn35.136:1.16":"dhammanam samudayanca atthangamanca assadanca adinavanca nissarananca yathabhutam viditva na dhammaramo, na dhammarato, na dhammasammudito. ","sn35.136:1.17":"Dhammaviparinamaviraganirodha sukho, bhikkhave, tathagato viharati”. ","sn35.136:1.18":"Idamavoca bhagava. ","sn35.136:1.19":"Idam vatvana sugato athaparam etadavoca sattha: ","sn35.136:2.1":"“Rupa sadda rasa gandha, ","sn35.136:2.2":"phassa dhamma ca kevala; ","sn35.136:2.3":"Ittha kanta manapa ca, ","sn35.136:2.4":"yavatatthiti vuccati. ","sn35.136:3.1":"Sadevakassa lokassa, ","sn35.136:3.2":"ete vo sukhasammata; ","sn35.136:3.3":"Yattha cete nirujjhanti, ","sn35.136:3.4":"tam tesam dukkhasammatam. ","sn35.136:4.1":"Sukham ditthamariyebhi, ","sn35.136:4.2":"sakkayassa nirodhanam; ","sn35.136:4.3":"Paccanikamidam hoti, ","sn35.136:4.4":"sabbalokena passatam. ","sn35.136:5.1":"Yam pare sukhato ahu, ","sn35.136:5.2":"tadariya ahu dukkhato; ","sn35.136:5.3":"Yam pare dukkhato ahu, ","sn35.136:5.4":"tadariya sukhato vidu. ","sn35.136:6.1":"Passa dhammam durajanam, ","sn35.136:6.2":"sammulhettha aviddasu; ","sn35.136:6.3":"Nivutanam tamo hoti, ","sn35.136:6.4":"andhakaro apassatam. ","sn35.136:7.1":"Satanca vivatam hoti, ","sn35.136:7.2":"aloko passatamiva; ","sn35.136:7.3":"Santike na vijananti, ","sn35.136:7.4":"magga dhammassa akovida. ","sn35.136:8.1":"Bhavaragaparetebhi, ","sn35.136:8.2":"bhavaraganusaribhi; ","sn35.136:8.3":"Maradheyyanupannehi, ","sn35.136:8.4":"nayam dhammo susambudho. ","sn35.136:9.1":"Ko nu annatra mariyebhi, ","sn35.136:9.2":"Padam sambuddhumarahati; ","sn35.136:9.3":"Yam padam sammadannaya, ","sn35.136:9.4":"Parinibbanti anasava”ti. ","sn35.136:9.5":"Tatiyam. "}